{ White to play and draw! }
1. Rh6+! Ka7 2. Qb6+! Rxb6 3. axb6+! Ka6 (3... Ka8 4. b7+ Ka7 5. Ra6+ Kxa6 6. b8=N+) 4. b7+! Ka7 (4... Ka5 5. Ra6+ Kxa6 (5... Kb4 6. b8=Q) 6. b8=N+) 5. Ra6+!! Kxa6 6. b8=N+!! Kb6 (6... Ka7 7. Nc6+) (6... Ka5 7. Nc6+) 7. Nd7+ { And white wins the black queen! (1/2-1/2) } *


