[ChapterMode "gamebook"]

{ White to play and win! }
1. Ne8! Kg6 (1... Rxh4 2. Ng7+ Kg6 3. Bf5#) (1... f5 2. Bxf5 gxh4 3. Ng7#) 2. h5+! Rxh5 (2... Kxh5 3. Ng7+ Kg6 4. Bf5#) 3. f5+! Rxf5 4. g4! Rf4 5. Bf5+! Rxf5 6. Ng7!! { We've reached a very picturesque position, where the white g-pawn will capture one of the black rooks on the next move with mate! } 6... Rd5 7. gxh5# { And black is checkmated! (1-0) } *


